    %h3 Background
    %p
      Nomads Of Code/Craft Academy (run by Adaptive Labs Nordic AB (559330-5005) Gothenburg, Sweden)
      (below “Nomads Of Code/Craft Academy”) is an educational platform for education of computer programming through teacher-led
      courses (“Courses”) which also works in tight connection with the industry in order to be able to create job
      opportunities for all students accepted to Nomads Of Code/Craft Academy for education (“Students”).

    %h3 Applicability
