    %h3 Fees
    %h4 Deposits
    %p
      All Students must pay a non-refundable deposit to secure their place on a Course. The deposit is payable upon online registration or at any other later stage decided by Nomads Of Code/Craft Academy before the Course starts and will be deducted from the total Course fee. Nomads Of Code/Craft Academy operates a “first come first served” policy so once you have paid your deposit we will reserve a place for you on our next available Course (subject to your payment of the Course fees in accordance with these Terms).
    %h4 Types of fees
    %p
