    %p
      Students can currently choose one of two possible payment options as described below:
    %h5 1. The standard payment option
    %p
      You pay the full fee for the Course (with deduction for already paid deposits) so that the payment is received by Nomads Of Code/Craft Academy not later than 14 days prior to commencement of the Course.
    %h5 2. Monthly payment option
    %p
      Nomads Of Code/Craft Academy offers a monthly payment plan through a financial third party provider. By choosing this option you will spread out the payment of the Course fee, including the deposit, over a longer period in time. The time and the conditions for repayment are chosen by you when you register for the Course and choose your payment option.
    %p
      Choosing this option will add costs to the Course fee due to fees added by the financial third party provider in accordance with the price list presented by Nomads Of Code/Craft Academy and the provider. By choosing this option you will also be bound by the conditions of the financial third party provider directly and enter into an agreement regarding payment with such third party, in which Nomads Of Code/Craft Academy will not be a party. Any payments shall in such cases be made directly to such party instead of Nomads Of Code/Craft Academy, unless otherwise specifically instructed to you in writing by Nomads Of Code/Craft Academy.
    %h4 Payments
    %p
