    %h4 Refunds
    %p
      Notwithstanding what option of payment that is chosen by you, by commencing as a Student to the Course, the entire Course fee is considered accrued to Nomads Of Code/Craft Academy even if a certain part of the fee is outstanding due to a payment plan option, meaning that you will not be refunded the Course fee if you are suspended or excluded from the Course pursuant to these Terms. Furthermore, if you fail to complete a Course due to any other reason than stated in these Terms, Nomads Of Code/Craft Academy reserves the right, in its sole discretion, to charge you the full amount of the outstanding fees immediately following confirmation that you will not be completing the Course. In exceptional circumstances Nomads Of Code/Craft Academy may, in its sole discretion, agree to waive payment of part or all of the outstanding fees.
    %p
      You may only be refunded the Course fee provided the Course in which you are enrolled is cancelled (whether prior to the course commencing, or after its commencement) by Nomads Of Code/Craft Academy, in which case any Course fee that has been paid by you will be refunded in full. If a Course is temporarily suspended for a period of less than one month no course fees will be refunded. If a Course is suspended for a period longer than one month Students enrolled on that Course will be given the option of continuing the Course when it resumes or receiving a pro-rata refund of Course fees for the suspended part of the Course (based on the number of full weeks of the Course that was suspended, as a percentage of the total number of course weeks).
    %h3 Right to study
    %p
      You must have the right to study in Sweden under applicable rules and hold an applicable and valid where necessary. As a general rule you will not need a visa if you hold a passport issued by any country in the EU or the European Economic Area (EEA). International Students are required to upon registration for a Course produce a passport, visa and/or any other related documentation necessary for studying or staying in Sweden. Nomads Of Code/Craft Academy may, at its sole discretion, reject an application for enrolment in a Course if Nomads Of Code/Craft Academy considers that the documentation does not fulfill applicable legal requirements.
    %p
